{"tid":647092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷之前向英國國家重案署舉報689，此事無下文。","createTime":"2018-04-29T14:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T00:15:22.000Z","uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1efad6ac8e1dcd9e5544ae82fcdb4185b18d04f","tid":647092,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"林卓延失威了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇來大家要捐夠689萬，林卓廷先做到野。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷之前向英國國家重案署舉報689，並委託英國大律師以證明案件屬於英方管轄範圍，此事再無下文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180429/mobile/bkn-20180429173944278-0429_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180429%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180429173944278-0429_00822_001.html&d=sSYdjU7C7ik4kpV3FL79f9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7f446388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180429/mobile/bkn-20180429173944278-0429_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3cc2a7dc703000c027bc3203c0ee52cf375e92bb","tid":647092,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d8a5de44cf62b168e84cbfea13bacd73eed39c3","tid":647092,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:15:22.000Z","msg":"科水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}